    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This unit delivers linear power through a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M differential lock for exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing adjustable damping rates that remain crisp and responsive. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and new throttle actuators, addressing the primary concerns for this platform. The subframe bushings and suspension geometry remain within factory spec, ensuring a precise, analog driving experience. A well-maintained example of BMW M's naturally aspirated peak.",
