      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained sedan that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free environment; the leather upholstery is soft and free of tears, showing only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s side. All interior technology, including the navigation system, heated seats, and sunroof, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is in great shape. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and the most recent inspection confirmed that the suspension is tight and the brakes have over 70% life remaining. The engine runs quietly with no leaks or warning lights on the dashboard. It currently rides on premium Michelin tires with substantial tread depth. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter. Clean title and service records available.",
